These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-1::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, zinnia, daisy, orchid, balloon-flower
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, subway, motorbike, bike
1. the person driving the helicopter is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the person who growsorchid##7
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
4. the person who growsbegonia is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
6. the person driving the bike is somewhere between the person who growszinnia and the person who growsdaisy##7
7. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person who growsorchid##5
8. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bus##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |        2        |      3       |     4      |      5      |
| Flower           | orchid | daisy | balloon-flower | zinnia | begonia    |
| Transport   | helicopter      | bus          | bike   | motorbike     | subway |

