.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: family, action, comedy, time-travel, disaster
House: palace, wooden, farmhouse, gothic-revival, art-deco
1. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##5
2. the person watching disaster movies is between the person watching action movies and the gothic-revival house##2
3. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
4. the art-deco house is on the far right##1
5. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
6. the palace house is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere between the person watching time-travel movies and the wooden house##7
8. the person watching family movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |   3    |     4     |   5   |
| Movie-Genre        | family | action | disaster | comedy | time-travel  |
| House   | palace   | wooden   | farmhouse | gothic-revival     | art-deco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-3::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, brown, emerald, mauve, lilac
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: snowboarding, cricket, lacrosse, badminton, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who likes red##1
2. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's sport is badminton##7
4. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
5. the person who likes red is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
8. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |     4     |    5    |
| Color          | emerald  | lilac   | mauve | brown      | red |
| Sport   | cricket | lacrosse | snowboarding   | badminton | weightlifting  |

