2. the police-officer is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the turtle is somewhere between the police-officer and the librarian##7
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
5. the analyst is on the left of the librarian##1
6. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
7. the designer is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |    5     |
| Job   | analyst | librarian | lawyer | designer    | police-officer |
| Pet     | rabbit     | ferret     | fish | turtle | pony     |

