.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-7::.
5 different games are played: bridge, whist, chess, poker, backgammon
The people have 5 different jobs:  musician, pilot, dressmaker, manager, fisherman
 1. the fisherman is not the person playing poker##6
 2. the person playing bridge is somewhere between the dressmaker and the fisherman##7
 3. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
 4. the manager is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 5. the pilot is on the left of the musician##1
 6. the person playing whist is the dressmaker##1
 7. the fisherman is the person playing chess##1
 8. the manager is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
 9. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing chess##1
10. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the manager##3
11. the pilot is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |   2   |       3       |      4      |   5    |
| Game   | poker | backgammon | whist | bridge | chess  |
| Job        | pilot     | musician   | dressmaker          | manager    | fisherman |

