.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-8::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, may, august, june, april
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: mystery, musical, fantasy, disaster, martial-arts
1. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
2. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the person watching martial-arts movies##7
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
6. the person watching musical movies is not the person who's birthday is in december##6
7. the person who's birthday is in december is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
9. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |    3     |  4  |   5    |
| Birthday   | august    | december | may | april | june |
| Movie-Genre        | musical | martial-arts      | fantasy    | mystery | disaster    |

