 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is not the person watching spy movies##6
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere between the person watching spy movies and the person who's hobby is skydiving##7
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
 8. the person watching western movies is not the person who's hobby is chess##6
 9. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
10. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
11. the person watching mystery movies is not the person who's hobby is chess##6
12. the person watching mystery movies is not the person who's hobby is skydiving##6
13. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person watching spy movies##1

